{"tid":1374087,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"學術討論：如果罷工，最好是一個星期左右的預備時間","createTime":"2019-07-27T17:11:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T03:16:12.000Z","uid":278712,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e4ea5e8c33dac67bd0516345da20eddaaeac22f3","tid":1374087,"uid":278712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:11:26.000Z","msg":"香港人返工的心態很重，除了<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">安全感</span></strong>，也是自小灌輸的<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">責任感</span></strong>。<br />\n所以需要時間去解釋。<br />\n定了日子後，<ins><strong>傳播</strong></ins>開去大約要<strong><ins>兩至三天</ins></strong>。<br />\n每個人<strong><ins>自己思考</ins></strong>又要<ins><strong>兩至三天</strong></ins>。<br />\n然後還會看看其他人的想法，<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">畢竟如果附和的人少，不單危險，而且沒用</span></strong>，所以又要<ins><strong>兩至三天溝通討論</strong></ins>。<br />\n如果想成功，反而不能要求每一個人都承受大風險，這不現實。<br />\n整個過程感覺最快也要<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">1星期左右</span></strong>，成功率才較高。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">不妨思考一下自己和身邊的人的情況，如果要通知和勸服他們，要多久時間？</span></strong>"},{"pid":"584aae95cb2c6599d497f408354077b32d19492a","tid":1374087,"uid":38737,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:12:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">8月5日 全港大罷工</span></span>"},{"pid":"4500af2716a639c37de508ecd4559633f2e0d67d","tid":1374087,"uid":66305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"584aae95cb2c6599d497f408354077b32d19492a","tid":1374087,"uid":38737,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:12:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">8月5日 全港大罷工</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:12:54.000Z","msg":"支持！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0e4f6564bcf55cbaeaab70dc7d706fba20cea55","tid":1374087,"